1457
01:35:34,750 --> 01:35:37,416
<i>Cheng Yih promised</i>
<i>we'll keep seeing each other.</i>

1458
01:35:38,083 --> 01:35:39,208
<i>But we will just be a bit</i>

1459
01:35:39,291 --> 01:35:40,708
<i>farther apart.</i>

1460
01:35:41,458 --> 01:35:42,708
<i>We worked hard to keep it going.</i>

1461
01:35:42,791 --> 01:35:44,583
<i>We stayed in a relationship.</i>

1462
01:35:46,250 --> 01:35:47,125
<i>I wonder</i>

1463
01:35:47,208 --> 01:35:49,208
<i>if I'd done too much</i>
<i>to go after Cheng Yih.</i>

1464
01:35:49,875 --> 01:35:52,333
<i>So much that I was 13 hours ahead.</i>

1465
01:35:53,458 --> 01:35:55,083
<i>I became Cheng Yih's future,</i>

1466
01:35:55,833 --> 01:35:58,958
<i>and he became my past.</i>

1467
01:35:59,541 --> 01:36:01,666
