- <i>Good job.</i>

1473
01:36:15,833 --> 01:36:16,958
- Look.
- <i>Very cute.</i>

1474
01:36:17,458 --> 01:36:18,500
<i>Hello. How are you?</i>

1475
01:36:18,583 --> 01:36:19,583
