1519
01:38:43,250 --> 01:38:45,875
<i>We still joked around sometimes,</i>

1520
01:38:47,458 --> 01:38:48,958
<i>until we both</i>

1521
01:38:49,041 --> 01:38:51,250
<i>faded out of each other's life.</i>

1522
01:38:54,041 --> 01:38:55,666
<i>We didn't break up.</i>

1523
01:38:55,750 --> 01:38:57,166
