1524
01:38:57,750 --> 01:38:58,791
<i>No tears were shed.</i>

1525
01:38:58,875 --> 01:39:00,041
<i>No arguments either.</i>

1526
01:39:00,541 --> 01:39:03,083
<i>We didn't break up as others would.</i>

1527
01:39:03,916 --> 01:39:06,166
<i>It was as if</i>
<i>our relationship never started,</i>

1528
01:39:06,250 --> 01:39:07,708
