1561
01:40:32,875 --> 01:40:34,166
<i>It's good in a way.</i>

1562
01:40:35,083 --> 01:40:38,291
<i>At least, he's vanished from your life.</i>

1563
01:40:39,416 --> 01:40:40,583
<i>Come on.</i>

1564
01:40:41,583 --> 01:40:44,375
