1585
01:42:27,208 --> 01:42:29,166
<i>We didn't say goodbye.</i>

1586
01:42:29,250 --> 01:42:31,541
<i>Is he taking good care of you?</i>

1587
01:42:31,625 --> 01:42:33,583
<i>I thought I'd move on.</i>

1588
01:42:34,333 --> 01:42:36,250
<i>I wish you well.</i>

1589
01:42:37,000 --> 01:42:38,041
<i>You finally have someone</i>

1590
01:42:38,125 --> 01:42:39,708
<i>with you in your world.</i>

1591
01:42:40,416 --> 01:42:41,791
<i>I'm admiring from the outside,</i>

1592
01:42:41,875 --> 01:42:43,500
